### Introspect Bot
GET {{Karata.Bot.Host}}/api/bots/{{Karata.Bot.Slug}}
Accept: application/json

### Invite Bot
POST {{Karata.Bot.Host}}/api/bots/{{Karata.Bot.Slug}}/games
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json

{ 
  "room": "019cd7e3-3772-75f7-8b0f-f13c07afbfa9",
  "password": null
}